atics"," and ",[54,63,64],{},"science",". Alongside academics, I developed a strong passion for ",[54,67,68],{},"sports",", especially ",[54,71,72],{},"fencing",", a discipline that taught me ",[54,75,76],{},"focus, perseverance, and self-discipline",".",[50,79,80,81,84,85,88,89,61,92,77,95,98,99,102],{},"During ",[54,82,83],{},"middle school",", I continued to explore my interest in science and technology while staying active in sports. ",[54,86,87],{},"Fencing"," remained an important part of my life, helping me develop a sense of ",[54,90,91],{},"rigor",[54,93,94],{},"commitment",[96,97],"br",{},"\nAt the same time, I deepened my understanding of ",[54,100,101],{},"core academic subjects",", building strong analytical and problem-solving skills.",[50,104,105,106,109,110,113,114,117],{},"In ",[54,107,108],{},"high school",", this growing passion naturally guided me toward a ",[54,111,112],{},"scientific path",", strengthening both my academic foundations and my desire to pursue ",[54,115,116],{},"engineering studies"," in higher education.",{"title":119,"searchDepth":120,"depth":120,"links":121},"",2,[122],{"id":47,"depth":120,"text":48},"Completed my high school education at Lycée Gustave Courbet in Belfort, France, earning a Baccalauréat Scientifique with honors.","md",{},true,{"title":10,"description":123},"dj8w9RiedZceh9sZnFWVSpB5FzL7Q4WnFpTDeRuRrPQ",[130,131],null,{"title":14,"path":15,"stem":16,"description":132,"children":-1},"A three-year program providing a complete foundation in computer science, mathematics, and digital technologies.",1773409595571]